WEBVTT

00:12:28.960 --> 00:12:33.136
Copa tjeter e letres thote,
"Per shkakun tim u krijua bota."

00:12:33.160 --> 00:12:36.280
Eshte tregimi i te vertetes qe une nuk
mund te bej gjithcka,

00:12:37.040 --> 00:12:39.240
por me siguri mund te bej dicka.

00:12:40.160 --> 00:12:41.816
Une mund te fal.

00:12:41.840 --> 00:12:43.040
Une mund te dashuroj.

00:12:43.560 --> 00:12:45.056
Une mund te dalloj.

00:12:45.080 --> 00:12:46.696
Une mund te protestoj.

00:12:46.720 --> 00:12:49.896
Une mund te jem pjese e kesaj bisede.

00:12:49.920 --> 00:12:52.776
Qe tani ne kemi nje rit fetar,

00:12:52.800 --> 00:12:54.016
nje qendrim,

00:12:54.040 --> 00:12:57.736
qe mban paradoksin mes
pafuqise dhe fuqise.

00:12:57.760 --> 00:12:58.976
Ne komunitetin hebre,

00:12:59.000 --> 00:13:02.296
koha e vetme ne te gjithe vitin,
qe ne gjunjezohemi plotesisht ne toke